      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior power delivery. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a responsive suspension geometry that minimizes body roll. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the mechanical vitals are optimized for peak lateral acceleration and throttle response.",
